OL,5,Cschizophrenia
OL,7,FA Plymouth man who stabbed his mother
OL,8,Fto death has been given an indefinite
OL,9,Fhospital order for manslaughter by
OL,10,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,12,FBradley Huggins, 25, carried out a
OL,13,Fbrutal and fatal knife attack on 53-
OL,14,Fyear-old Hazel Huggins after she went
OL,15,Fto help clean his flat. He stabbed her
OL,16,F11 times.
