OL,3,CMan stabbed 'cherished' mother to
OL,4,Cdeath while suffering from
OL,5,Cschizophrenia
OL,7,FHuggins, who suffers with various
OL,8,Fmental health conditions, had made
OL,9,Fprevious threats towards his parents
OL,10,Fbut acted that day after a dispute
OL,11,Fover money.
OL,13,FAfter the killing, Huggins phoned
OL,14,Fpolice and then confessed his crime to
OL,15,Fhis father through a series of
OL,16,FWhatsApp messages.
OL,18,FHuggins pleaded guilty to manslaughter
OL,19,Fby diminished responsibility at an
OL,20,Fearlier hearing and was sentenced on
OL,21,FMonday 13 May at Plymouth Crown Court.
