OL,7,FExpert psychiatric reports compiled
OL,8,Fafter the incident identified that
OL,9,FHuggins had been suffering from
OL,10,Fschizophrenia at the time of the
OL,11,Fattack on his mother.
OL,13,FOn Saturday 29 July 2023, he had asked
OL,14,Fhis mum to help deep clean his Ilbert
OL,15,FStreet flat as he believed he had
OL,16,Fcontracted a contagious infection.
OL,18,FShe was dropped off around 11.30am by
OL,19,Fher husband and Bradley's father Guy
OL,20,FHuggins, who arranged to collect her
OL,21,Fat 4pm.
