OL,7,FThat afternoon Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,FPolice received two 999 calls.
OL,10,FThe first was made at 4.11pm by
OL,11,FBradley Huggins who was talking in a
OL,12,Flow voice, swearing, and not making
OL,13,Fhimself clear.
OL,15,FFour minutes later Guy Huggins called
OL,16,F999 to express concern for his wife
OL,17,Fwho he had been fruitlessly calling
OL,18,Fsince 3.40pm. He had driven to the
OL,19,Fflat but there was no reply.
