OL,7,FArmed officers forced entry to the
OL,8,Fflat, finding Mrs Huggins fatally
OL,9,Finjured.
OL,11,FThe knife was located on a coffee
OL,12,Ftable in the living room and Bradley
OL,13,FHuggins was standing by the window
OL,14,Fwith his hood up and wearing a
OL,15,Fsurgical mask. He was arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murder and admitted to
OL,17,Fofficers that he had killed his mother.
OL,19,FDetectives from the Force Major Crime
OL,20,FInvestigation Team launched a murder
OL,21,Fenquiry.
