OL,7,FA post mortem concluded that Mrs
OL,8,FHuggins died from 11 stab wounds to
OL,9,Fher neck, chest and abdomen.
OL,11,FHuggins was initially charged with
OL,12,Fmurder but his plea of guilty to
OL,13,Fmanslaughter by diminished
OL,14,Fresponsibility was accepted by the
OL,15,Fcourt at a hearing on 28 March.
