OL,7,FDetective Inspector Neil Blanchard
OL,8,Ffrom the Major Crime Investigation
OL,9,FTeam said: "This is a terribly sad and
OL,10,Ftragic case, and our thoughts remain
OL,11,Fvery much with family members who have
OL,12,Facted with grace and dignity
OL,13,Fthroughout the investigation.
OL,15,F"We have worked closely with the CPS
OL,16,Fand independent mental health experts
OL,17,Fwho concluded that Huggins was
OL,18,Fsuffering from schizophrenia when he
OL,19,Fattacked and killed his mother.
