OL,7,F"I would like to thank the
OL,8,Finvestigation team for their diligence
OL,9,Fand hard work on this case and I hope
OL,10,Ftoday's outcome brings a measure of
OL,11,Fpeace for the family."
OL,13,FOn behalf of the family Mr Guy Huggins
OL,14,Fpaid tribute to Hazel Huggins, saying:
OL,15,F"Following the sentencing of Brad
OL,16,FHuggins today, we continue to grapple
OL,17,Fwith the profound loss of our beloved
OL,18,FHazel, my amazing wife and mother to
OL,19,Fmy two sons.
