OL,7,F"She was a cherished member of our
OL,8,Fextended family and a precious friend
OL,9,F- a beacon of kindness, faith, joy,
OL,10,Fand love in our community and beyond.
OL,11,FHazel's radiant spirit touched the
OL,12,Flives of many as she lived out her
OL,13,FChristian faith.
OL,15,F"Today we encountered evidence for the
OL,16,Ffirst time which we will need time to
OL,17,Fprocess as we grieve. The events of
OL,18,FJuly 29, 2023, will forever be etched
OL,19,Fin our hearts as a day of unimaginable
OL,20,Ftragedy.
