OL,7,F"Brad's actions were the result of
OL,8,Fsevere mental illness. We find
OL,9,Fourselves sharing a tragic bond with
OL,10,Ffar too many families who have
OL,11,Fsuffered similar bereavements either
OL,12,Fat the hands of mentally ill
OL,13,Frelatives, or by strangers known to
OL,14,Fhave serious mental health conditions.
OL,16,F"Hazel fought for Brad, she loved him,
OL,17,Fand she could not have done more to
OL,18,Fhelp and support him.
