OL,7,F"We would like to extend our deepest
OL,8,Fgratitude to Devon and Cornwall
OL,9,FPolice, the CPS, our police family
OL,10,Fliaison officers, Victim Support, and
OL,11,FJoin the Dots Solutions for their
OL,12,Funwavering support and dedication
OL,13,Fthroughout this ordeal.
OL,15,F"I don't know how people get through
OL,16,Fevents and traumas like this without a
OL,17,Ffaith. In the midst of our deep
OL,18,Fsorrow, we draw strength and comfort
OL,19,Fthrough our Christian faith and the
OL,20,Foutpouring of prayers and support from
OL,21,Faround the world.
