OL,7,F"Hazel's death will never be
OL,8,Fforgotten, and has impacted many
OL,9,Fpeople, but we choose to forgive my
OL,10,Feldest son Brad and to advocate for
OL,11,Fhim to receive the medical care and
OL,12,Fsupport that he desperately needs.
OL,14,F"Hazel was, and always will be, "a
OL,15,Fbright shining light, loved by many".
OL,16,FShe was not only my wife, she was also
OL,17,Fmy soul mate, and I miss her so, so
OL,18,Fmuch."
